name: Creating a new AMS raptor item for different Eval types and simulate grading for each

elements.name: Author creates a "Relation" type "2x+26=0" equation and verifies grading for correct answer "2x+26=0" input

steps.name: I login to AMS as "all-permissions-author"
I click on the New Raptor item in the AMS page
I navigate to AuthorApp tab
I select Graded equation and save as "Relation"
I click on the Question tab, and add an Answer field
I set the grade as "Relation" type, with "", "", "" and input "2x+26=0"
I save the question and verify saving message box
I am in Take Mode and input the correct "2x+26=0"
I simulate grading
My answer is graded correctly
